Package researcherInfoSys

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Input
    A utility class with several static methods to load Excel file and get user input.
    KmeansModel
    A helper class to realize K-Means Clustering algorithm, and recommend similar researchers to a specified researcher.
    Main
    Entrance of the program.
    Researcher
    Stores data for a researcher, and contains a repository of all researcher as well, by which a series of functionalities can be realized.
    Similarity
    A utility class which provide different kind of indicators to measure similarity between two instances, including cosineSimilarity and KL divergence currently.
    Test
    A class providing a command line interface for users to test Task 1-6
    Timer
    A utility class for measuring the time elapsed.
    TopicModel
    A helper class to implement Probabilistic Topic Model and recommend similar researchers to a specified researcher.
